{"tid":526741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣行政院賴長清德狗年賀卡曝光　閩南語漢字盼「做伙拍拚」","createTime":"2018-01-12T02:18:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-12T09:35:26.000Z","uid":35790,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f58d922fe13831c36a260fd853e14de6a6df3d7e","tid":526741,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T02:18:27.000Z","msg":"看過來！賴清德狗年賀卡曝光　閩南語漢字盼「做伙拍拚」<br />\n<br />\n2018/01/12 07:30<br />\n<br />\n行政院版賀年卡曝光！賴清德首度以行政院長身份寄送賀年卡，採用深紅色搭配金色字體，相當喜氣，立法院各立委昨天下午收到賴的新年賀卡。賴清德祝賀2018「土豐民樂」，相較過去中規中矩的祝賀用語，賴清德的賀詞採閩南語漢字與英文並列。，寫道「人講一家若同心，烏土嘛會變黃金，新的一年向望咱士農工商做伙拍拚，互相牽成，予臺灣成做一個閣較幸福的國家」。<br />\n今年的行政院賀卡走濃濃文青風，卡片封面採用2D狗頭側面燙金設計，封底則是印章陰刻設計的「土豐民樂」字樣。賴清德在卡片中還說，「春天的花芳已經來到門窗&hellip;舊年，勞力；來年，祝福土豐民樂，繼續向前行。」卡片上除了有賴清德中文簽名，他更簽上自己名字的羅馬拼音。<br />\n（張文馨／台北報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180112/640_df718ae2e41b8cc469cae0312ed99219.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180112%2F640_df718ae2e41b8cc469cae0312ed99219.jpg&h=332e4f53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180112/640_9f9dc574b0b8c6f20402d79b46c83eb1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180112%2F640_9f9dc574b0b8c6f20402d79b46c83eb1.jpg&h=4617a70f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180112/1276980/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180112%2F1276980%2F&d=%2F3u2QRHOOrReLkGe8io5ff9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=5380806d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180112%2F1276980%2F&h=1f015fe5\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180112/1276980/</a><br />\n<br />\n叫&quot;漢字&quot;唔係叫&quot;中文&quot;<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e144e16217f17f02460574b2329b54213a4cc2d","tid":526741,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T02:19:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d5c353f1e3bc811935b7f0e01c6f8770c6fed81","tid":526741,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T02:30:54.000Z","msg":"寫道「人講一家若同心，烏土嘛會變黃金，新的一年向望咱士農工商做伙拍拚，互相牽成，<span style=\"color: red;\">予臺灣成做一個閣較幸福的國家</span>」。<br />\n<br />\n成張賀卡無&quot;中華民國&quot;字樣"},{"pid":"9eef8221155d37fbc46476bbeb3fc2df12f52816","tid":526741,"uid":137134,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T06:03:03.000Z","msg":"又係d劣種台狗打飛機式獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一口流利普通話 用中文<br />\n仲夠膽死笑香港人係大陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好心d台狗認清事實啦 <br />\n國際上根本得台狗當台灣係一個獨立國家<br />\n台狗成日話「國外」「國內」<br />\n屌你老母笑撚大人個口咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n獨立左啦依家？<br />\n台狗個垃圾政府夠膽公開宣布獨立先算啦<br />\n希望有生之年睇到中共狗收撚返台狗<br />\n賤種台狗根本係繁體支那劣種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adc1c9d4c9357c4d5b6b9d28206bf308e1cc5430","tid":526741,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T09:35:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}